snippet.textDisplay:
I have been listening this music since three days mind soothing and heart touching music really  touch the soul comfort 
Coke studio always brings innovation in the art of music who has presented the whole philosophy of Sufism in few verses and worth of human being how to live and spend happy life with inner satisfaction . Every line is worthwhile and has deeper meanings for  deep listeners.
Nasebo and Abida API  has sung these verses with the core of heart and their voices are so attractive which bounds me to listen every second  .
Whenever I have unrest with this material I play this song and take take comfort .
